Package com.telenav.kivakit.resource.packages

Class ClasspathResource

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.kivakit.resource.packages.ClasspathResource
All Implemented Interfaces:
ResourcePathed, UriIdentified
public class ClasspathResource extends Object implements ResourcePathed
A resource on the classpath having the following attributes:

Attributes

  • asUri() - The URI to the resource
  • packageReference() - The package where the resource resides
  • javaPath() - The full package path to the resource
  • lastModified() - The time of the last modification to the resource
  • size() - The size of the resource
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
